  "title": "Production Support Technician中控/工艺/设备人员",
  "description": "<p>1.负责生产车间生产过程监控与操作，确保产线运行正常</p>\n<p>Monitor and operate the production process on the workshop floor to ensure smooth production line operation.</p>\n<p>2.负责生产车间设备的保养和维护，及时处理异常</p>\n<p>Perform routine maintenance and upkeep of production equipment, and promptly address any malfunctions</p>\n<p>3.负责工艺参数管理与优化，确保产品质量稳定</p>\n<p>Manage and optimize process parameters to ensure stable product quality.</p>\n<p>4.负责车间各岗位的协调与沟通，促进生产计划达成</p>\n<p>Coordinate and communicate between different workshop floor positions to facilitate the achievement of production plans.</p>\n<p>5.负责生产数据记录与报表</p>\n<p>Record production data and generate relevant reports.</p>\n<p>技能要求：</p>\n<p>1.计算机与软件技能</p>\n<p>Computer and software skills, proficiency in common office software.</p>\n<p>2.熟悉常规设备原理，了解自动化控制系统的基本操作与维护</p>\n<p>Familiar with the principles of conventional equipment; basic knowledge of operating and maintaining automation control systems. e.g., PLC(Programmable Logic Controller),DCS(Distributed Control System).</p>\n<p>3.质量与安全意识</p>\n<p>Strong quality and safety awareness.</p>\n<p>4.分析与应变能力</p>\n<p>Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.</p>\n<p>5.沟通与团队合作</p>\n<p>Good communication and teamwork skills.</p>\n<p>6.自动化/机电等专业 大专及以上</p>\n<p>Diploma or above in Automation, Mechatronics, or related fields</p>",
